p136
aVone day I was in the office in Peshawar, Pakistan.
p137
aVAll of a sudden, I saw my staff running to rooms and locking the doors
p138
aVand telling me, "Run away, hide!"
p139
aVAnd you know, as a leader, what do you do?
p140
aVYou're scared. You know it's dangerous.
p141
aVYou know your life is on the line.
p142
aVBut as a leader, you have to hold it together.
p143
aVYou have to hold it together and show strength.
p144
aVSo I said, "What's going on?"
